    ],
    "category": "Formula",
    "text": "$$\n\\text{Ta có } T(x; y) = \\frac{1}{10} + \\frac{\\sqrt{0,6^2 + x^2}}{6} + \\frac{0,5-x}{10} + \\frac{\\sqrt{0,6^2 + y^2}}{6} + \\frac{0,5-y}{10} = \\frac{1}{10} + f(x) + f(y).\n$$"
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
      211,
      378,
      929,
      475
    ],
    "category": "Formula",
    "text": "$$\n\\text{Xét hàm số: } f(u) = \\frac{\\sqrt{0,6^2 + u^2}}{6} + \\frac{0,5-u}{10}, \\quad 0 < u < 1.\n$$"
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
      211,
