      1222,
      577
    ],
    "category": "Formula",
    "text": "$$\n\\text{Ta có: } f'(u) = \\frac{u}{6\\sqrt{0,6^2 + u^2}} - \\frac{1}{10}, \\quad f'(u) = 0 \\Leftrightarrow \\sqrt{0,6^2 + u^2} = \\frac{5u}{3} \\Leftrightarrow u = \\frac{9}{20}.\n$$"
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
