    "text": "$$\n\\text{Do đó } T(x; y) = \\frac{1}{10} + f(x) + f(y) \\ge \\frac{1}{10} + \\frac{13}{100} + \\frac{13}{100} = \\frac{9}{25}(h) = 21,6 \\text{ (phút).}\n$$"
